## ER диаграмма для Statistic Service

```mermaid
erDiagram
  STATISTIC {
    int id PK
    int post_id FK
    string event_type
    int user_id FK
    datetime event_time
  }

  DAILY_STATISTIC {
    date event_date
    int post_id FK
    int likes_count
    int views_count
    int comments_count
  }

  USER_STATISTIC {
    int user_id FK
    int total_likes
    int total_views
    int total_comments
  }

